        "subject": "LU-11526 rpc: support maximum 32MB I/O RPC",
        "message": "LU-11526 rpc: support maximum 32MB I/O RPC\n\nIn the new SFA, the block driver allows 32768 max_hw_sector_kb\n(32MB) from vOSS (SFA embeded stack) to SFA below. To maximize\ndriver efficiency, Lustre should also have bump up maximum I/O\nRPC size to 32MB.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I511d93ef61278fdf95774cbf3535f1a8cf4c9efa\n"
      },
